# Empathy-Map-on-McDonald-s
An Empathy map is a visual tool used to understand a user's attitudes and behaviors by exploring what they say,think.do, and feel.
For McDonald's , this tool helps design teams and marketers step into the customer's shoes to create more user-centric experiences, products, and services.
